{"id":232823166,"title":"衣櫃除濕劑作法?","content":"因為最近有些木頭東西想放衣櫃，必須要控制濕度 (希望能在50~60%)\n想請問各位是如何在衣櫃中除溼? (衣櫃大小約 1m*2m*0.6m，不算小)\n\n平時房間不會一直開著除溼機，大約兩天開一次除一下，但只要一沒開很容易濕度就上去70%、80%。\n有想過買迷你除溼機放裡面，但除濕機產品關在櫃子裡一直開心裡有點怕....\n\n目前想到的辦法是買小米或台灣牌的水玻璃的除濕器，插電可以恢復再繼續除溼，不知有沒有人使用過或者能提供其他建議??謝謝\n\n小米牌\n1) 這款要220V\nhttp://i.imgur.com/rW81p4E.jpg\n\n2)這款可以110v\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/ZTkRE0g.jpg\n\n3) 台灣廠牌\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/TVSkieG.jpg","excerpt":"因為最近有些木頭東西想放衣櫃，必須要控制濕度 （希望能在50~60%），想請問各位是如何在衣櫃中除溼？ （衣櫃大小約 1m*2m*0.6m，不算小），平時房間不會一直開著除溼機，大約兩天開一次除一下，","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"5b964198-2e59-419d-b44c-0276d0fea7e8","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-04T07:53:15.834Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-04T07:53:15.834Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":2,"tags":[],"topics":["衣櫃","除溼"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"居家生活","forumAlias":"house","school":"銘傳大學","department":"國際企業學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":2}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/rW81p4E.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/ZTkRE0g.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/TVSkieG.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"4e6857e1-5dfb-41fc-94ad-a237805fc572","url":"https://i.imgur.com/rW81p4El.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/rW81p4El.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/rW81p4El.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-04T07:53:15.834Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-04T07:53:15.834Z"},{"id":"4e6857e1-5dfb-41fc-94ad-a237805fc572","url":"http://i.imgur.com/rW81p4E.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/rW81p4E","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/rW81p4El.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-04T07:53:15.834Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-04T